title: The U.K. Supreme Court has struck down a plan to send asylum-seekers to Rwanda
description: In a major defeat for the British prime minister, the Supreme Court has ruled the government's migrant plan is unlawful and would put asylum-seekers at risk of deportation back home.

title: Clouds made of sand make for a strange kind of rain on this hot planet
description: On Earth, clouds and rain are made of water. But the James Webb Space Telescope has found that on a planet called WASP-107b, the rain and clouds are made of sand.
